title: The Budos Band - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents The Budos Band performing live at THING Festival at Fort Warden in Port Townsend, Washington. Recorded August 25, 2023

Songs:
Frontier’s Edge
Crescent Blade
Long in the Tooth
Gun Metal Grey

Andrew Greene - Trumpet 
Eric Biondo - Trumpet 
Jared Tankel - Sax
Daniel Foder - Bass
Brian Profilio - Drums

Host: DJ Morgan

Mastering: Matt Ogaz
